decoding="async"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="170"
data-flex-basis="408px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>An inbound call which is intended for a delegator but forwarded to delegates will look like this.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/pick-up-held-and-join-active-calls-for-boss-delegate-scenarios-in-microsoft-teams-4cb1d4965424/1m2B6ebHrfMX34ckn1Yn6hQ.png"
