>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>For the record, this is how it looked in the old Teams client.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/pick-up-held-and-join-active-calls-for-boss-delegate-scenarios-in-microsoft-teams-4cb1d4965424/1lMmaHnyIl0angFvf7VXw.png"
width="452"
