&lt;p>This works in the opposite direction too. If Wendy answers a call which was forwarded to her by Mike and puts that call on hold, Mike will be able to pick up the call.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://heusser.pro/p/pick-up-held-and-join-active-calls-for-boss-delegate-scenarios-in-microsoft-teams-4cb1d4965424/17fiLpMRJ8LxJy0XNpvLoQ.png"
